Package us.dahp.spellsapi.models

Class AbstractSpell

java.lang.Object
us.dahp.spellsapi.models.AbstractSpell
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractSelfSpell, AbstractSurroundSpell
public abstract class AbstractSpell
extends Object
General spell class. This should be extended when creating a standard spell that casts at a target.
Since:
04/10/2020
Author:
sirNikolai

      public abstract void impactEntities​(org.bukkit.entity.Player caster, float multiplier, List<org.bukkit.entity.LivingEntity> entities)

      multiplier - The spell multiplier.
